(78, 1, '2015-02-16 07:33:38', '2015-02-16 07:33:38', 'Powerful tools from start to finish\r\nRace IT provides premium online solutions for event directors across the country. Race IT utilizes a unique combination of strategic thinking, creative vision, and technological experience to provide powerful online registration features that are intuitive and easy to use.\r\n\r\nWant to learn more about our features?\r\nTake a look below', 'Event Organizers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'event-organizers', '', '', '2015-02-16 08:18:57', '2015-02-16 08:18:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/raceit/?page_id=78', 0, 'page', '', 0),
