nd would like to change it or remove it from our records, simply contact us at information@RaceIT.com and we will delete the information.\r\n\r\nWe do not share children’s personal information with anyone other than those who fulfill the registrations performed via our web site (e.g., league administrators, race directors).\r\n\r\nParental Review\r\nParents can review the information that we have collected from their children online, prevent the further use or maintenance of such information, or direct the deletion of their children’s personal information by:\r\n\r\ncalling us at the telephone number provided above\r\ne-mailing us at the above address\r\nwriting to us at the above address\r\ninformation@RaceIT.com', 'Child Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-16 08:22:17', '2015-02-16 08:22:17', '', 82, 'http://localhost/raceit/82-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
